└─
```

## With a tuple argument

```catala-metadata
declaration min_assoc
  content (integer, anything of type t)
  depends on l content list of (integer, anything of type t)
  equals
    content of (i, x) among l such that i is minimum
#      or if list empty then (0, impossible)
```


```catala
#[test]
declaration scope C:
  output r content (integer, money)

scope C:
  definition r equals
    min_assoc of
      [(1, $3); (44, $2); (2, $1); (3, $2); (-1, $5); (100, $100); (0, $10)]

```

```catala-test-cli
